    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a pure analog driving experience with exceptional lateral grip and telepathic throttle response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
