    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained executive sedan offers a perfect balance of performance and luxury. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though there are minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway commuting. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. Mechanically, the vehicle is sound; it features a complete service record, a recently replaced battery, and tires with significant tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly, and the cabin remains whisper-quiet at speed. While one alloy wheel has slight curb rash, the overall presentation is professional and clean. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
