    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s been well-maintained and still looks great inside and out. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to find a new owner who will love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
