      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. It features a factory M-Variable differential lock and has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS service. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by Bilstein dampers, maintaining exceptional damping rates and roll control. While the exterior reflects its history as a driven machine, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering linear power delivery and the signature metallic rasp of the individual throttle bodies. A mechanically sound driver's car ready for the canyon roads.",
